    "body": "``` yaml\nGTMTNK:\n    Inherits: ^Tank\n    Valued:\n        Cost: 500\n    Tooltip:\n        Name: Archon Tank\n    Buildable:\n        Queue: Vehicle\n        BuildPaletteOrder: 10\n        Prerequisites: ~gaweap, ~!t1\n    Mobile:\n        Speed: 56\n        ROT: 5\n        Crushes: wall, crate, infantry\n    Health:\n        HP: 400\n    Armor:\n        Type: Light\n    RevealsShroud:\n        Range: 6c0\n    Turreted:\n        ROT: 3\n    Armament@PRIMARY:\n        Weapon: 90mm\n        LocalOffset: 900,0,500\n        MuzzleSequence: muzzle\n    AttackTurreted:\n    AutoTarget:\n    RenderSprites:\n    RenderVoxels:\n        NormalsPalette: RA2normals\n    WithVoxelBody:\n    WithVoxelTurret:\n    WithMuzzleFlash:\n```\n\nIn RA the offset is calculated correct, while in TS it's not working like intended. This problem is also happening to vanilla units in the TS mod. 4TNK for example.\n\nExisting templates from default.yaml haven't been changed.\n"
